accesor functions for objects of CBSResult S4 class, minimal parent class for SecretSanat outputs

accesor functions for objects of CBSResult S4 class, minimal parent class for SecretSanat outputs

Accessors for CBSResult objects

setInfasta(theObject, in_fasta)

# S4 method for CBSResult
setInfasta(theObject, in_fasta)

# S4 method for CBSResult
getInfasta(theObject)

# S4 method for CBSResult
setOutfasta(theObject, out_fasta)

# S4 method for CBSResult
getOutfasta(theObject)

Arguments

theObject

CBSResult object
in_fasta

input fasta, AAStringSet object
out_fasta

output fasta, AAStringSet object

Value

CBSREsult object

Slots

in_fasta

initial fasta file

out_fasta

output fasta with only positive candidates, i.e those that passed tool filters

Examples

# read fasta file in AAStringSet object
aa <- readAAStringSet(system.file("extdata","sample_prot_100.fasta",
                        package = "SecretSanta"))
# create an instance of CBSResult class:
cbs <- CBSResult( in_fasta = aa, out_fasta = aa)
# check that CBSResult instance is valid
validObject(cbs)
#> [1] TRUE

# extract in_fasta attribute
getInfasta(cbs)
